data.description: *** SELLER IS OFFERING $10,000 towards paint and flooring, repairs or interest rate buydown! ***  5 Bedroom, 3 full bath, 2 car garage home backing onto conservation. Are you looking to lower your electric bill? This home comes with PAID OFF solar panels that are owned and a whole home water softener. These are a $50,000 value! This home has so much space and lots of potential. Features include a flex room when you walk in the front door and also a loft/flex room upstairs giving you lots of options for office and family areas, recessed lighting, ceiling fans in most rooms, large bedrooms, laundry room upstairs, guest room + full bathroom on the main level, and storage under the stairs. The kitchen offers an island with eating space and a corner walk in pantry. The master suite is huge, with a large walk in closet, dual sinks and a large walk in shower. Enjoy the Florida lifestyle in your large yard with no back yard neighbors, overlooking a county preserve. A great location with two community dog parks, 5 houses down the street. Cypress Creek is a master planned community that includes a clubhouse with a pool and a fitness center. Conveniently located near I-75, US Hwy 301 and US Hwy 41 easily accessible to all that Tampa, St. Pete and Sarasota have to offer. Major retail centers include Sun City Center, Ruskin and Riverview, with a large library branch just up the road. Book your private tour today!
